# Architecture

SYNC consists of four major components.

## SYNC iOS

The production application.

Creates portable human-authorization receipts using Apple's platform security technologies.

Responsibilities include:

• Intent capture

• Evidence attachment

• Device authorization

• Receipt generation

• Export

---

## Receipt Format

Portable receipt object containing:

• Human intent

• Evidence manifest

• Authorization metadata

• Time

• Policy context

• Chain metadata

• Cryptographic integrity

Receipt exports are designed for long-term portability and independent verification.

---

## OpenVerifier

Independent verification implementation.

OpenVerifier reconstructs canonical receipt material directly from exported receipts.

Verification intentionally separates independent guarantees rather than collapsing them into a single result.

Verification includes:

• Content integrity

• Signature verification

• Issuer recognition

• Evidence manifest integrity

• Receipt structure validation

• Chain metadata evaluation

